title: volunteer V01 at time point T0
source_name_ch1: A PBMC sample from volunteer V01 at time point T0
treatment_protocol_ch1: PBMC samples are collected at various time points during a malaria vaccine trial
extract_protocol_ch1: Trizol extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the GeneArray Scanner
description: Gene expression data from a volunteer V01 at time point: Baseline;it belongs to NonProtected group
data_processing: CEL files were normalized using RMA method. This dataset was further normalized with a dataset from Plus2.0 Genechip using quantiles normalization method available in the affy package of bioconductor. Probesets that are absent in all samples are eliminated in the later stage of analysis
contact_institute: Walter Reed Army Institute of Research
